 bulk-boundary correspondence. We study several\ntight binding models to quantitatively check the relation between the extra\ncharge accumulation and the inter-cellular Zak phase as well as the\nbulk-boundary correspondence using the inter-cellular Zak phase.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Aug 2016 20:02:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-30"}
