ted from random\nprobabilistic marginal queries as means to compare other tractable\nprobabilistic models on a common ground, extending our experiments to Mixtures\nof Trees.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Aug 2016 22:10:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 24 Aug 2018 16:27:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-27"}
