in this framework we can predict that regulatory systems will\nevolutionary favor networks where the number of catalytic enhancers is not\nlarger than the number of suppressors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 30 Aug 2016 15:23:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-08-31"}
